        <abstract>
            <p>Glad CD likes his Presidential Address to Geological Society [1863].</p>
            <p>Will continue the practice [of discussing the break in succession of strata].</p>
            <p>Has devised a diagram showing number of genera and species in each geological formation and the number that pass from formation to formation.</p>
            <p>Describes the glaciated terrain of S. Wales.</p>
        </abstract>
